'''Temple Gate Polytechnic''' is a pioneer private [[Nigerian]] tertiary institution that is accredited by the [[National Board for Technical Education]].<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.sunnewsonline.com/new/abia-poly-pledges-to-address-nigerias-manpower-needs/ | title=Abia poly pledges to address Nigeria’s manpower needs | work=[[The Sun (Nigeria)|The Sun]] | author=Sampson,Okey | date=15 May 2015 | accessdate=12 September 2015 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925074116/http://sunnewsonline.com/new/abia-poly-pledges-to-address-nigerias-manpower-needs/ | archivedate=25 September 2015 | df= }}</ref> The polytechnic is located in [[Aba, Nigeria|Aba]], [[Abia State]] and it offers [[National Diploma (United Kingdom)|National Diploma]] and [[Higher Diploma]] courses in [[undergraduate]] levels.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.templegatepolytechnic.com/mission/ | title=Mission | publisher=Temple Gate Polytechnic | accessdate=12 September 2015}}</ref>
