The '''Windhoek College of Education''' (now known as the University of Namibia Khomasdal campus) is public university in [[Khomasdal]], [[Windhoek]], [[Namibia]]. It opened in 1978 and is one of four national colleges of education.<ref>[http://www.wce.edu.na/page.php?p=about Windhoek College of Education] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110104075809/http://www.wce.edu.na/page.php?p=about |date=2011-01-04 }}</ref>
